CommentBody:
In today's meeting, we reviewed the current system and toke some screenshots.
We made a backup of the job folder and the webserver.exe
We will upgrade the application to the latest version in the next meeting.

I upgraded StealthAUDIT from 11.5.0.240 to 11.6.0.92 version. We also updated the Access Information Center and the Sensitive Data Add-on to the latest version.
We assigned the certificate to the Publish Report site and ensured the AIC remain secured.
The customer requested a meeting because the Yes or No button to approve a request did not work. Once I met with the customer, he said everything was working fine, so we could close this ticket.
